These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, trance, disco
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | electronic | disco | trance |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: prague, venice, boston, london
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to prague is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | london    | prague | boston | venice    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | sprite | 7up | iced-tea    | soy-milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, 7up
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking 7up##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | coffee       | milk   | hot-chocolate    | 7up  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, swimming, skiing
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | soccer  | volleyball    | swimming   | skiing       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

