.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
House: cape-cod, colonial, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the colonial house is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| House   | futuristic | colonial     | cape-cod  | gothic-revival  |

