.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, french, argentine, turkish
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the french##3
2. the turkish is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the turkish##3
4. the turkish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the canadian is between the turkish and the french##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the canadian and the owner of the goat##2
8. the canadian is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Nationality   | french | canadian      | turkish | argentine |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

