.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, fonseca, siglo, tiparillo
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the siglo-smoker##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the siglo-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | fonseca   | prince | siglo |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

