.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, librarian, entrepreneur, journalist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the coach is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the coach##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the entrepreneur##2
4. the coach is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the librarian is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Job      | librarian       | entrepreneur   | coach | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

