.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, hamster, bird
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | chess         | board-games   | magic-tricks |
| Pet   | hamster    | mouse | bird | guinea-pig   |

