.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, pineapple, broccoli, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating potato##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
5. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
6. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | potato | broccoli    | apricot |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

