.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, train, scooter
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person driving the train##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport         | scooter   | train | jet-ski | motorbike    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

