.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, bike, van
There 4 different types of food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
3. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
7. the person eating corn is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | van | car    | bike       | jet-ski |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

