.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
City: hannover, berlin, marseilles, miami
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, tram, trike
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| City   | berlin | marseilles | hannover  | miami |
| Transport     | bus      | tram       | motorbike | trike     |

