.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
House: farmhouse, futuristic, victorian, palace
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the futuristic house is between the entrepreneur and the farmhouse house##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the victorian house is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the victorian house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| House   | palace          | futuristic | farmhouse         | victorian  |

 